Our artistes should make songs to encourage youths and society —Owens The Chief Executive Officer (CEO) of Money Making Machine Group (MMMG), Agbontan Godson is the owner of a popular lounge called Owens. He speaks to SEGUN KASALI about his record label and his assessment of the entertainment industry in the country. Our artistes should make songs to encourage youths and society —Owens  Source: Tribune